{"tid":2070240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人港地梁振英連日追擊　英華校長突傳請辭","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T04:27:34.000Z","uid":291865,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00bc8bb62d09afb38050ec845072b747e790d645","tid":2070240,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"有 200 多年歷史的傳統名校英華書院，陷入政治風暴。早前多名英華書院學生於操場和平悼念 6.15 逝世的抗爭者梁凌杰，事後被全國政協副主席梁振英及親建制網站《港人港地》大加批評。校方日前發通告，指不認同學生行為，校方一直秉持政治中立原則，反對任何「港獨」口號及言論，並指事發時已有老師從旁勸止，及按校本訓輔機制跟進。英華書院校長鄭鈞傑今天向校友透露，自己早於上月已向校監請辭，並於明年 8  月離任，到加拿大團聚；他並未透露自己離職和悼念事件是否有關。 《立場新聞》已向英華書院發電郵查詢事件，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n（已節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%93%8D%E5%A0%B4%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E6%A2%81%E5%87%8C%E6%9D%B0%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%96%8A%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E8%BF%BD%E6%93%8A-%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E7%AA%81%E5%82%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%BE%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%259D%25B0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2596%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%2593%258A-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25BE%25AD%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=9436859a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%259D%25B0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2596%258A%25E6%25B8%25